# Automated Bus Scheduling System — DTC

Full-stack system for managing bus schedules, driver duties, and route planning.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS + Leaflet.js
- Backend: Node.js + Express + MongoDB

## Features
- Linked and unlinked duty scheduling
- Automatic bus and driver conflict detection  
- Driver rest period management
- GIS route visualization with overlap detection
- Full CRUD for buses, drivers, routes, schedules

## Setup

### Backend
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev

### Frontend  
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev